1
00:00:33,500 --> 00:00:34,370
Never forget

2
00:00:34,500 --> 00:00:35,770
what this woman did.

3
00:00:36,170 --> 00:00:37,270
It's all her fault

4
00:00:37,540 --> 00:00:39,270
that I've become so paranoid.

5
00:00:39,440 --> 00:00:40,540
It's all her fault

6
00:00:41,010 --> 00:00:42,110
that I can't

7
00:00:42,110 --> 00:00:43,180
fall for anyone ever again.

8
00:00:48,680 --> 00:00:51,150
I'm going to make her life

9
00:00:51,150 --> 00:00:52,420
a living hell!

10
00:01:19,550 --> 00:01:20,850
No one saw us, right?

11
00:01:21,250 --> 00:01:22,580
I don't think so.

12
00:01:22,680 --> 00:01:25,490
Ugh! This is such a pain!

13
00:01:25,490 --> 00:01:26,890
It can't be helped.

14
00:01:26,890 --> 00:01:29,520
You are a huge
superstar, after all.

15
00:01:29,790 --> 00:01:31,890
I wish we could hold hands
and walk outside.

16
00:01:31,890 --> 00:01:33,130
We can't.

17
00:01:33,130 --> 00:01:35,360
Who knows what would happen
if we got caught again.

18
00:01:35,360 --> 00:01:36,860
We'd get so many strange looks...

19
00:01:36,860 --> 00:01:38,130
you know?

20
00:01:39,130 --> 00:01:41,370
That's true.

21
00:01:43,400 --> 00:01:48,840
I want to...
touch your hand, too...

22
00:01:48,840 --> 00:01:49,840
My hand.

23
00:01:50,310 --> 00:01:51,640
Not hold it.

24
00:01:51,950 --> 00:01:53,210
Touch it.

25
00:01:55,420 --> 00:01:56,420
That sounds kind of pervy.

26
00:01:59,620 --> 00:02:00,620
No.

27
00:02:03,490 --> 00:02:05,630
I won't lose.

28
00:02:06,630 --> 00:02:08,060
Lose to what?

29
00:02:10,230 --> 00:02:12,130
I don't know either.

30
00:02:12,730 --> 00:02:14,300
But I just don't want to lose.

31
00:02:20,140 --> 00:02:21,240
So cute.
